ygData.messageBody:
2 questions . . . I am a gnome necromancer . ..

1) Can I go to the bank in freeport and get money for necro guild or will I be KOS in bank zone. (Ins't the bank in North Freeport?)

2) If I wanted to play it safe, get my money from Akkanon bank then take boat to Freeport, HOW DO I GET to the NECROGUILD from the outside. So guy told me there is a passage from the wall in west free port that goes into the necro guild from outside and I was wondering if anyone could give me specifics on oing this.
